 py-2 transition-smooth\">Events</button></a><a href=\"/join\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-10 px-4 py-2 transition-smooth\">Join Us</button></a></div><div class=\"flex md:hidden items-center absolute right-4\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-10 w-10\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></nav><section class=\"relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-white snap-start\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-white overflow-hidden\"><canvas class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full\"></canvas></div><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-transparent z-0 pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center mt-16\"><div class=\"animate-fade-in-up\"><div class=\"mb-6 flex justify-center\"><img src=\"/ethbcc_logo.png\" alt=\"ETHBCC Logo\" class=\"h-20 w-auto transition-smooth hover:scale-105\"/></div><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 text-foreground/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light\">We connect strong industry partners to driven students, fostering education, innovation, and collaboration in Blockchain technology.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\"><a href=\"/join\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 rounded-md px-8 gradient-primary shadow-elegant hover:shadow-medium transition-calm group\">Join Us<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 h-5 w-5 transition-smooth group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button></a><a href=\"/events\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 border bg-background hover:text-accent-foreground h-11 rounded-md px-8 border-primary/30 hover:bg-primary/5 transition-calm\">See Events</button></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center animate-fade-in\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light-title mb-6 text-gray-800\">Our Vision</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r gradient-primary mx-auto\"></div></div><p class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">We aim to positively shape the future of blockchain technology by educating tomorrow&#x27;s innovators.<br/>Through Education, Events, and Industry Collaboration, we build technical expertise, expand practical knowledge, and foster responsible innovation to advance real-world adoption.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light-title mb-6 text-gray-800\">What We Do</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r gradient-primary mx-auto\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-8 shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-graduation-cap h-6 w-6 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.42 10.922a1 1 0 0 0-.019-1.838L12.83 5.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 9.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.832l8.57 3.908a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0z\"></path><path d=\"M22 10v6\"></path><path d=\"M6 12.5V16a6 3 0 0 0 12 0v-3.5\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\">Educational Workshops</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground\">We host and develop workshops to educate students, providing valueable knowledge and hands-on learning experiences.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-8 shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-6 w-6 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\">Big Events &amp; Hackathons</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground\">We organize regular events and hackathons with industry partners, creating opportunities for students to network, build, and showcase their projects.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-8 shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users h-6 w-6 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744\"></path><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-3\">Industry Connections</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground\">We foster direct connections between students and industry leaders through partnerships, mentorship programs, and career opportunities that transform learning into real-world impact.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light-title mb-6 text-gray-800\">Academic Collaborations</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r gradient-primary mx-auto\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">DBB</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Dr. Bastian Bergmann</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Lecturer and Executive Director of the FinsureTech Hub, ETH Zürich</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">As founding mentor, he has provided invaluable guidance, mentorship and support.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">PDAG</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Prof. Dr. Arthur Gervais</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Professor of Information Security, University College London</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">As founding supporter, he has provided essential academic insights, mentorship and transformative opportunities.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light-title mb-6 text-gray-800\">Advisors</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r gradient-primary mx-auto\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">J</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Jerome</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Branding Advisor</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground shadow-sm p-6 text-center shadow-glass hover:shadow-elegant transition-smooth group bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 overflow-hidden group-hover:scale-110 transition-smooth\"><div class=\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold\">A</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg mb-1 text-primary\">Adrian</h3><p class=\"text-primary text-sm mb-3 font-medium\" style=\"color:hsl(199 100% 35%)\">Strategic Advisor</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-white\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light-title mb-6 text-gray-800\">Open For Collaboration</h2><div class=\"w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r gradient-primary mx-auto\"></div></div><p class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8\">As an accredited student club at ETH Zurich, we bring together a community of driven and curious minds eager to collaborate. Led by dedicated students, we embody ETH Zurich&#x27;s spirit of innovation and problem-solving. Ranked 7th globally and the top university in continental Europe (QS World University Rankings 2025), ETH Zurich provides the perfect environment for partnerships that push boundaries and create real impact.</p><a href=\"/collaborate\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 rounded-md px-8 gradient-primary shadow-elegant hover:shadow-medium transition-calm group\">Collaborate with Us<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 h-5 w-5 transition-smooth group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button></a></div></div></section><footer class=\"bg-muted/30 border-t border-border mt-20\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center space-y-4 md:col-span-2\"><div class=\"flex justify-center\"><img src=\"/ethbcc_logo.png\" alt=\"ETHBCC Logo\" class=\"h-4 w-auto\"/></div><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground text-center\">Building the future of decentralized innovation at ETH Zurich.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-center md:text-left\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold\">Quick Links</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"